DEPENDANCIES
============

Adam Dependancies
-----------------
* libc++

Vstore Module Dependancies
--------------------------
 * unixodbc
 * libodbc
 * sqlite odbc driver


SETUP
=====

/etc/sudoers:
-------------

www-data ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: /usr/bin/pkill, NOPASSWD: /usr/local/adam/bin/adam, NOPASSWD: /bin/kill, NOPASSWD: /bin/echo, NOPASSWD: /usr/local/adam/tools/vstore2dump

/etc/odbc.ini (vstore)
----------------------

[vstore_sqlite]
Description=Adam/Visible Hand Vstore database
Driver=SQLite3
Database=/usr/local/adam/admin/data/vstore.sqlite
# optional lock timeout in milliseconds
Timeout=2000

